{"tid":1578847,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"裕美條新仔王志康入左TVB做主播","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T03:31:06.000Z","uid":324078,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ee79e76266c3565194d42c2566192d79d08f82b7","tid":1578847,"uid":324078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"有旅遊達人之稱的王志康（Hiroki），近日正式加盟成為邵氏兄弟旗下經理人合約及無綫電視藝人，成為陳瀅及方力申同門師弟，簽約後首項工作是擔任TVB娛樂新聞台主播。他很感激樂易玲小姐讓他加入邵氏，及綜藝部監製給予機會。其實他是TVB第二十六期藝員訓練班畢業生，三年前他因為希望完成學業，故前往日本升學，畢業於日本東京國際大學，因而成為「日本通」，更變身成旅遊網紅。 <br />\n<br />\nHiroki指這次能夠返回TVB，除了思想變得成熟不少，更會比別人加倍努力工作：「三年前停低咗腳步，為未來作出準備，今日人生再次向新目標進發，展開新旅程，會用十倍努力工作，用謙卑嘅心從頭學起，努力做好每件事。」他指當初入訓練班的目標是做一位出色主持，故現在能夠加入娛樂新聞台非常開心：「以前細細個就幻想自己係娛樂新聞主播，距離夢想好似行近咗，會好好珍惜呢個機會。」又表示做主持可令自己的口才、臨場反應有改善，對自己是一個好訓練。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190812/bkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190812%2Fbkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001.html&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=75b1d748\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190812/bkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190630/photo/bkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190630082817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190630%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190630082817&h=9ca2b393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放棄幕前去咗日本東京國際大學讀咗三年。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190630/photo/bkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190630082817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190630%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190630082817&h=2dd48997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗完成學業仲變咗「日本通」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190630/photo/bkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190630082817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190630%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190630082817&h=1cccbee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次重返TVB~ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190630/photo/bkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190630082817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190630%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190630051452089-0630_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190630082817&h=9de9dbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王志康話會用十倍努力做好工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190812/photo/bkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001_06b.jpg?20190812041828\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20190812041828&h=41f15235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目標係做個出色嘅主持。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/e2Gxt3W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2Gxt3W.jpg&h=29166842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190812/photo/bkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001_08b.jpg?20190812041828\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190812041615334-0812_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20190812041828&h=23c13cd